						<summary>

						<p>Records the gift of six <hi rend="italic">uttamagaṇḍa-māḍas</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Nemmalūri Sūraya</hi> for the upkeep of a perpetual lamp in the temple of Agastīśvara of <hi rend="bold">Kommūru.</hi> The endowment was to be administered by the three hundred <hi rend="bold">Sānis</hi> of Kommūru.</p>						

